{"id":780,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":780,"title":"Jeremiah 11","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 11"],[".studySummary",["i","The people of Judah are cursed for breaking the covenant of obedience—The Lord will not hear their prayers."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.1","order":"02.25.011.51531"},["b","1"],"The word that came to Jeremiah from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.2","order":"02.25.011.51532"},["b","2"],"Hear ye the words of this covenant, and speak unto the men of Judah, and to the inhabitants of Jerusalem;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.3","order":"02.25.011.51533"},["b","3"],"And say thou unto them, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Cursed"],["i","be"],"the man that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"obeyeth not"],"the words of this",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"covenant"],","],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.4","order":"02.25.011.51534"},["b","4"],"Which I commanded your fathers in the day",["i","that"],"I brought them forth out of the land of Egypt, from the iron furnace, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Obey"],"my voice, and do them, according to all which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"I"],"command you: so shall ye be my people, and I will be your God:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.5","order":"02.25.011.51535"},["b","5"],"That I may perform the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"oath"],"which I have sworn unto your fathers, to give them a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"land"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"flowing"],"with milk and honey, as",["i","it is"],"this day. Then answered I, and said, So be it, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.6","order":"02.25.011.51536"},["b","6"],"Then the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto me, Proclaim all these words in the cities of Judah, and in the streets of Jerusalem, saying, Hear ye the words of this covenant, and do them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.7","order":"02.25.011.51537"},["b","7"],"For I earnestly",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"protested"],"unto your fathers in the day",["i","that"],"I brought them up out of the land of Egypt,",["i","even"],"unto this day, rising early and protesting, saying, Obey my voice."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.8","order":"02.25.011.51538"},["b","8"],"Yet they obeyed not, nor inclined their ear, but walked every one in the imagination of their evil heart: therefore I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"will bring"],"upon them all the words of this covenant, which I commanded",["i","them"],"to do; but they did",["i","them"],"not."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.9","order":"02.25.011.51539"},["b","9"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto me, A",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"conspiracy"],"is found among the men of Judah, and among the inhabitants of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.10","order":"02.25.011.51540"},["b","10"],"They are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"turned"],"back to the iniquities of their forefathers, which refused to hear my words; and they went after other gods to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"serve"],"them: the house of Israel and the house of Judah have broken my covenant which I made with their fathers."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.11","order":"02.25.011.51541"},["b","11"],"¶Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Behold, I will bring",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"evil"],"upon them, which they shall not be able to escape; and though they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"cry"],"unto me, I will not hearken unto them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.12","order":"02.25.011.51542"},["b","12"],"Then shall the cities of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem go, and cry unto the gods unto whom they offer incense: but they shall not save them at all in the time of their trouble."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.13","order":"02.25.011.51543"},["b","13"],"For",["i","according to"],"the number of thy cities were thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"gods"],", O Judah; and",["i","according to"],"the number of the streets of Jerusalem have ye set up altars to",["i","that"],"shameful thing,",["i","even"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"altars"],"to burn incense unto Baal."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.14","order":"02.25.011.51544"},["b","14"],"Therefore",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"pray"],"not thou for this people, neither lift up a cry or prayer for them: for I will not hear",["i","them"],"in the time that they cry unto me for their trouble."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.15","order":"02.25.011.51545"},["b","15"],"What hath my beloved to do in mine house,",["i","seeing"],"she hath wrought lewdness with many, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"the"],"holy flesh is passed from thee? when thou doest evil, then thou rejoicest."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.16","order":"02.25.011.51546"},["b","16"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"called thy name, A",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"green"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"olive tree"],", fair,",["i","and"],"of goodly fruit: with the noise of a great tumult he hath kindled fire upon it, and the branches of it are broken."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.17","order":"02.25.011.51547"},["b","17"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, that planted thee, hath pronounced evil against thee, for the evil of the house of Israel and of the house of Judah, which they have done against themselves to provoke me to anger in offering incense unto Baal."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.18","order":"02.25.011.51548"},["b","18"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath given me knowledge",["i","of it,"],"and I know",["i","it:"],"then thou shewedst me their doings."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19","order":"02.25.011.51549"},["b","19"],"But I",["i","was"],"like a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"lamb"],["i","or"],"an ox",["i","that"],"is brought to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"slaughter"],"; and I knew not that they had",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"devised"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"devices"],"against me,",["i","saying,"],"Let us destroy the tree with the fruit thereof, and let us",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_19e"},"cut him off"],"from the land of the living, that his name may be no more remembered."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.20","order":"02.25.011.51550"},["b","20"],"But, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, that judgest righteously, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"triest"],"the reins and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"heart"],", let me see thy vengeance on them: for unto thee have I revealed my cause."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.21","order":"02.25.011.51551"},["b","21"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of the men of Anathoth, that seek thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"life"],", saying, Prophesy not in the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that thou die not by our hand:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.22","order":"02.25.011.51552"},["b","22"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, Behold, I will punish them: the young men shall die by the sword; their sons and their daughters shall die by famine:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.23","order":"02.25.011.51553"},["b","23"],"And there shall be no remnant of them: for I will bring evil upon the men of Anathoth,",["i","even"],"the year of their visitation."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.3a","order":"02.25.011.51554"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.3b","order":"02.25.011.51556"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.3c","order":"02.25.011.51558"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.20.1-26"},"Ex. 20:20 (1–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.4a","order":"02.25.011.51560"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"TG Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.4b","order":"02.25.011.51562"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.38.37-41"},"Alma 5:38 (37–41)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.5a","order":"02.25.011.51564"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/7.12.12-13"},"Deut. 7:12 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.20"},"D&C 38:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.5b","order":"02.25.011.51566"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-land-of"},"TG Israel, Land of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.5c","order":"02.25.011.51568"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.8"},"Ex. 3:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.7a","order":"02.25.011.51570"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"witnessed."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.8a","order":"02.25.011.51572"},["b","8a"],["span.small","OR"],"brought."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.9a","order":"02.25.011.51574"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conspiracy"},"TG Conspiracy"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.10a","order":"02.25.011.51576"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.6"},"Zeph. 1:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.10b","order":"02.25.011.51578"},["b","10b"],["span.small","OR"],"worship."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.11a","order":"02.25.011.51580"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/punish"},"TG Punish"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.11b","order":"02.25.011.51582"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/18.41.40-41"},"Ps. 18:41 (40–41)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21.15"},"Mosiah 21:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.7"},"D&C 101:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-access-to"},"TG God, Access to"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.13a","order":"02.25.011.51584"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.13b","order":"02.25.011.51586"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"TG Apostasy of Israel"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.14a","order":"02.25.011.51588"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.16"},"Jer. 7:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.11"},"14:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.15a","order":"02.25.011.51590"},["b","15a"],["span.small","IE"],"acceptable sacrifice has ceased."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.16a","order":"02.25.011.51592"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/52.8"},"Ps. 52:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.16b","order":"02.25.011.51594"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vineyard-of-the-lord"},"TG Vineyard of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19a","order":"02.25.011.51596"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/53.7"},"Isa. 53:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/14.7"},"Mosiah 14:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/135.4"},"D&C 135:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19b","order":"02.25.011.51598"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19c","order":"02.25.011.51600"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"TG Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19d","order":"02.25.011.51602"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.62.60-62"},"Lam. 3:62 (60–62)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.19e","order":"02.25.011.51604"},["b","19e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/83.4"},"Ps. 83:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.20"},"1 Ne. 1:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.20a","order":"02.25.011.51606"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.20b","order":"02.25.011.51608"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.34"},"D&C 64:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.21a","order":"02.25.011.51610"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"TG Prophets, Rejection of"],"."]]}
